Thanks<br>
/rude hell levels<br>
<br>
*EDIT* I also tried the dorfs by the BB docks, great xp but the faction hit is bad. Any other suggestions of places like that but without a bad faction hit? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rynar>Rynar</A> at: 6/30/01 7:18:35 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genadiel>Genadiel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/30/01 12:13:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Happ</span><hr size=1> Hmm, you must have had an off night because I was went from 47 to 48 on Happ yesterday very easily. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
To break the camp (when she has her pet), I cast Immobilize on the pet.  I then quickly target her and cast Conflagration which quickly brings her down to 1/3 health.  She'll either try to cast again or come running - in any event, I cast Ice Shock and she's dead.  Don't have to worry about the pet since it now aggros one of the other gnomes heh.<br>
<br>
From then on she's easy.  You'll quickly recognize a pattern when she spawns on her casts.  Immediately upon spawning she'll cast a DS on herself.  If you cast conflag right after, she'll start to cast another DS on a fellow gnome right as conflag hits her.  She'll channel through her spell while you are busy casting a lower DD to finish her off.  Easy easy.  Pick up this pattern and you have easy exp.<br>
<br>
I had a couple of resists, and she punched me a while - nothing steelskin can't handle.  I channeled through 98% of her nukes/melees.  ONE time out of yesterday I had to zone when she resisted conflag/immobilize and harassing me with doubles of 90. =P  Otherwise, easy camp with nice exp.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps.<br>
<br>
Genadiel Jadenstar<br>
48 Wiz of Fallen Gods<br>
